 (targeted for T-030), and the use of the `Event` model for these transformations is the correct adaptation for the current project state.\\n+\\n+## Security\\n+No security vulnerabilities or unsafe practices were introduced. The implementation consists of pure-function mathematical transformations on local data structures.\\n+\\n+## Quality\\n+The code quality is high, with clear documentation, clean dataclass abstractions, and robust role-parsing logic. The tests use Pearson correlation to verify complementarity, which is a rigorous approach for validating musical behavior.\\n+\\n+## Issues Found\\n+- None.\\n+\\n+## Verdict: PASS\\n+\\n+## Notes for Lead Agent\\n+The implementation successfully realizes the call-response gating requirement. The adaptation to use the `Event` model in the absence of `PerformanceIntent` is appropriate. Recurring hardening checks for `bootstrap_identity` were also verified to be satisfied in the current daemon startup paths.\\n+\\n+ succeeded in 0ms:\\n+# Verification\\n+\\n+## Summary\\n+Auto-synthesized from verifier output because the canonical verification report was not written.\\n+\\n+## Issues Found\\n+_Verifier did not provide a structured Issues Found section; see Notes for Lead Agent._\\n+\\n+## Notes for Lead Agent\\n+{\\\"type\\\":\\\"init\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-04-17T04:03:47.303Z\\\",\\\"session_id\\\":\\\"2084b1a1-4576-4146-afcb-5707affb146b\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"gemini-3-flash-preview\\\"}\\n+{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-04-17T04:03:47.734Z\\\",\\\"role\\\":\\\"user\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"# Verification: Task T-024@20260416T181925Z\\\\n\\\\n**Task:** Implement R11 Call-Response Gating: follower phrase intent complements leader's realized performance.\\\\n**Tier:** T1\\\\n\\\\nYou are the VERIFY agent for this task. The LEAD agent has completed their work.\\\\n\\\\n## Acceptance Criteria\\\\n\\\\n- `render/rules/call_response.py` reads leader voice's PerformedPart and transforms fol