my-claw/sdp/prd-federation-proposal-writes.md:16:| FEDWRITE-002 | Implement target-home approval gating for every cross-home mutation. No mutation request may execute until the target home approves it locally. | MUST | T1 | - Unapproved proposals cannot mutate local state<br/>- Approved proposals execute locally on the target home<br/>- Approval decision is auditable |
